      *                  * Valore della variabile                      *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      s-num                to   w-ipc-tpv-ftf-val      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Uscita                                      *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           go to     ipc-tpv-ftf-999.
       ipc-tpv-ftf-400.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se variabile non esistente                      *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Segnale di variabile non esistente          *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "N"                  to   w-ipc-tpv-ftf-snx      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Valore della variabile a zero               *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      zero                 to   w-ipc-tpv-ftf-val      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Uscita                                      *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           go to     ipc-tpv-ftf-999.
       ipc-tpv-ftf-999.
           exit.

